    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1889-11-17T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1889-11-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="37"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d37">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adams</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Blaine</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Rio de Janeiro</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1889-11-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">November</hi> 17, 1889</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Imperial family sailed to-day. Government <hi rend="italic">de facto</hi>, with
                    ministry, established. Perfect order maintained. Important we acknowledge
                    Republic first.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Adams.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
